{"tid":334273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【人見人憎】共享單車強霸車位 台灣民眾堆疊入公廁洩憤","createTime":"2017-07-24T14:21:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T14:40:25.000Z","uid":79563,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f8da6f65217fa6c99dd633a934e7db5a81f9a9aa","tid":334273,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:21:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170724/large/1500901131_779d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170724%2Flarge%2F1500901131_779d.jpg&h=f83b7eda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣的共享單車，不但強佔各地的電單車位，引來民眾不滿，近日更有網民發現有人將這些共享單車踩至新北八里的觀音山，之後拋棄在山上，部份更被堆疊在公廁內。<br />\n<br />\n北海岸及觀音山國家風景區管理處指出，這些共享單車在本月9日突然出現在觀音山風景區內，但都放置在公享單車格及電單車格內。前來觀音山遊憩的民眾準備停車時見到車格被佔用十分不滿，疑似因此才將單車堆疊推倒，還有民眾將單車搬移至公廁堆置。<br />\n<br />\n管理處批評，共享單車的原意是好，可是業者未與景區協調，就直接將單車搬上山，造成民眾不便與不滿。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》"},{"pid":"bf64080775fc706863d85d0d9ec40e0acfa1ec7c","tid":334273,"uid":4494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:23:07.000Z","msg":"繁體大陸"},{"pid":"732dc07ffd14efdfb460c6c093910fa378edf9cf","tid":334273,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:24:02.000Z","msg":"台灣最美的是________"},{"pid":"4e433b19a2d251384a23b00c558c057492744fd0","tid":334273,"uid":71257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:27:57.000Z","msg":"連登仔支持以暴易暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c4d8d13a6c0d45a6e570006d4b2ce5d3062ab9","tid":334273,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:51:57.000Z","msg":"掉落城門河 vs 掉上山"},{"pid":"01447e885a4be54f307acce12ec648090e1fd44d","tid":334273,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:23:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>掉落城門河 vs 掉上山</blockquote><br />\n新加坡試過有人將啲單車入14樓高嘅走廊掉落街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\